text: Marie-Anne Vandermoere (born 10 September 1966) is a Belgian rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Belgium Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bruges
